==Nga ha Makwareala==
Shayandima ndi mudi uno wanala tshipembe-vhukovhela ha [[Thohoyandou]]. Shayandima a si kule na Thohoyandou lune muthu anga tshimbila nga milenzhe u bva Shayandima uya Thohoyandou. Dorobo khulwane dza tsini ndi [[Thohoyandou]], [[Sibasa]] na [[Louis Trichardt]].  

==Pfudzo==
Gudedzi la Tshidzini li wanala henefha Shayandima. Gudedzi ili ndi la ugudisa vhathu mushumo wa vhunese. Gudedzi ili li wanala tsini na vhuongelo ha [[Tshilidzini]].

==Vhadzulapo==
Vhunzhi ha vhathu vha no dzula afha vha amba tshiVenda.

==Mishumo==
Ha-Ramasaga (Shayandima Industrial Site) ndi hune vhathu vhanzhi vha Shayandima vha shuma hone. Vhanwe vha vhathu vha Shayandima vha shuma Thohoyandou.
